## Weaknesses

SAC Capital insider trading culture revealed compliance blind spots. Supervision failures allowed illegal information gathering. SEC enforcement removed $1.8B+ in assets. Overreliance on information edge creates legal/ethical risks. Pod competition can create siloing and lack of firm-wide coordination.

